@siemens/ix-icons

Getting started

  • Install npm install @siemens/ix-icons
  • Add "node_modules/@siemens/ix-icons/dist/scss/ix-icons.scss" to your angular.json - e.g "styles": ["node_modules/@siemens/ix-icons/dist/scss/ix-icons.scss"]
